name: Super Soaked
description:
At the end of 2020, I had a broken collar bone and could not paint with my dominant hand. My trigger finger, however was still fully functional. So I painted (sprayed) model, Sawyer Croft, with a paint in my Super Soakers!

Watch it on YOUTUBE https://youtu.be/WRtoQr_QdRY
